                        "type": "text",
                        "text": "Patriotic."
                      }
                    ]
                  },
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": " I am a loyal supporter of Phlan and its leaders, and see my role as a solemn duty and necessary evil to prevent anarchy. (Lawful)"
